      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s seriously like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken absolute pride in keeping it in pristine, mint condition, and honestly, you won\u2019t find a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh new-car smell that everyone loves. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been pampered and loved, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
