    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the marque, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a perfectly calibrated double-VANOS system. The vehicle exhibits zero subframe fatigue and retains its factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal torque vectoring. Every mechanical component, from the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to the original suspension geometry, remains in concours-level synchronization. With a pristine exterior and a powertrain that delivers its full 333hp output with surgical precision, this is an investment-grade specimen for the analog purist.",
