    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of a 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman, preserved in showroom condition. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, ensuring the Guards Red paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish free of any stone chips or swirls. The interior is indistinguishable from new, with the Black leather sport seats showing no signs of bolster wear, fading, or creasing. Mechanically, this Cayman is beyond reproach; it comes with a comprehensive binder of service records from authorized Porsche centers, including its most recent major service and fluid flush. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates precisely as intended. Included in the sale are both original keys, the factory window sticker, and a custom-fitted indoor car cover. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a modern classic that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
